    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "This looks good though how does instantsearch use nouislider? So for example how would I put \r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nnoUiSlider.create(pipsSteps, {\r\n\trange: range_all_sliders,\r\n\tstart: 0,\r\n\tpips: {\r\n\t\tmode: 'steps',\r\n\t\tdensity: 3,\r\n\t\tfilter: filter500,\r\n\t\tformat: wNumb({\r\n\t\t\tdecimals: 2,\r\n\t\t\tprefix: '$'\r\n\t\t})\r\n\t}\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\ninto the instantsearch?\r\n\r\nDo I need to use a specific param to send raw params to nouislider or should it just understand if I slap a new property in the widget defnition of `pips`?",
