    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Ok I actually got it working with:\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n\tinstantsearch.widgets.rangeSlider({\r\n\t\tcontainer: '#priceRange',\r\n\t\tattributeName: 'lp',\r\n\t\ttooltips: {\r\n\t\t\tformat: function(rawValue) {\r\n\t\t\t\treturn '£' + Math.round(rawValue).toLocaleString();\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t},\r\n\t\tpips: {\r\n\t\t\tmode: 'positions',\r\n\t\t\tvalues: [0,50,100],\r\n\t\t\tdensity: 3,\r\n\t\t\tformat: wNumb({\r\n\t\t\t\tdecimals: 0,\r\n\t\t\t\tprefix: '£'\r\n\t\t\t})\r\n\t\t},\r\n\t\ttemplates: {\r\n\t\t\theader: 'Price Range'\r\n\t\t},\r\n\t\tcssClasses: {\r\n\t\t\troot: 'panel panel-default quick-search-facet-panel',\r\n\t\t\theader: 'panel-heading',\r\n\t\t\tbody: 'panel-body'\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t})\r\n);\r\n```",
